      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "$46,500 - Mint-condition example that presents exceptionally well inside and out. It runs and drives exactly as it should, appears extremely well cared for, and shows only the slightest signs of age or use. The paint, interior, and overall presentation are far above average for its age, and it has the kind of clean, well-preserved feel buyers hope to find. Not described as brand new, but this is an outstanding, honest example that should impress anyone looking for a top-condition car.",
