    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at a hard-to-beat price point. It shows age and wear consistent with an older pre-owned vehicle, making it a smart choice for a budget-conscious buyer, first-time driver, or anyone needing inexpensive everyday mobility. Priced to sell and presented as an honest value opportunity.",
