      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly car with plenty of potential? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest old runner that could make a great project, spare vehicle, or cheap way to get around. It\u2019s priced to reflect that it needs some TLC, and for the right buyer there\u2019s real value here. If you\u2019re handy with cars or just want something affordable with character, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 4800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly car with good bones and plenty of usable life left. Starts, runs, and drives, with an engine that pulls cleanly and a drivetrain that feels serviceable for a daily, backup car, or project build. Condition reflects age and use, but it\u2019s a straightforward platform with practical utility and room to improve. If you want inexpensive transportation or a wrench-friendly car with potential, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car now. Used and rough, priced to move. First serious buyer takes it.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of old-school personality you notice the moment you walk up to it\u2014a lived-in, honest machine with plenty of story left to tell. It\u2019s the sort of ride that makes sense for someone who wants affordable wheels now, or a hands-on project with real charm and potential. There\u2019s a rugged, no-nonsense character here that\u2019s hard to fake, and for the right buyer, that\u2019s exactly the appeal: a chance to get into a vehicle with presence, purpose, and room to make it your own.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age and wear, but it starts, runs, and delivers straightforward value for someone seeking an inexpensive daily driver, backup vehicle, or project opportunity. A practical choice for buyers who want low upfront cost and room to make it their own.",
      "price": 4950.0,
